  <name>Sonic Robo Blast 2 Kart</name>
  <summary>A kart racing game based on the fangame Sonic Robo Blast 2</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Sonic Robo Blast 2 Kart (often shortened to SRB2Kart or SRB2K) is a
      fan-created kart racing game with retro graphics that play homage to
      pop-culture video game characters.  SRB2Kart features over 100 maps
      for two game modes: the main Race mode and a Battle mode where players
      fight each other using the items available in the game.
    </p>
